metadata.name: Autumn Morning
metadata.description:
Title: Autumn Morning  
Edition: 1/1  
Artist: James Andrew  
License: Extended Editorial

A morning walk through the local woodland. Breathing in the fresh autumn air, soaking in the sights and sounds of my favorite season. Autumn does not last long here, and I try and take it all in before the snow flies and the cold winter months set in.
